item.title: Not updateing
item.dc:creator: @bryanc Bryanc
item.description:
@bryanc wrote:

First get java. Jdk1.5.0_09 and Jre1.5.0_09 (jdk update 9) (jre or something) or read my last sentence posted.
then put this in your compiler in the ‘edit’ instead of what you got.

@echo off
title Sw00tscape Compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_09\bin/java.exe” server
pause

Or you can change the _09’s to what ever you have. Like _08 or something

~bryanc~
